\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The value of 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Lannister
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 is:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
V_{L}=V_{U}+D\cdot t_{c}=\frac{CF\cdot(1-t_{c})}{r_{U}}+D\cdot t_{c}=\frac{\$240K\cdot60\%}{12\%}+\$500K\cdot40\%
\]

